I'm trying to create an XPS file with this code:

```
using (var document = SKDocument.CreateXps(path + "test.xps"))
{
     using (var c = document.BeginPage(800, 1000))
     {
          item.Draw(c);
          document.EndPage();
     }

     document.Close();
}
```

But test.xps file can't be open until the application is closed. The same code with CreatePdf method instead of CreateXps works.
